## Environment Variables for Production Deployment

# Backend API URL (set in Vercel dashboard)
# Deploy backend first, then use its URL here
VITE_API_URL=https://your-surakshapay-backend.vercel.app

## Local Development (.env.local)
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8080

# Copy to .env.local for local dev, or set directly in Vercel project settings

